name: LEO
description: Roll out the red carpet because Leo has arrived. Leo is represented by the lion and these spirited fire signs are the kings and queens of the celestial jungle. They’re delighted to embrace their royal status: Vivacious, theatrical, and passionate, Leos love to bask in the spotlight and celebrate themselves. Bull run at the start of the week: you feel the situation is finally unlocking and working in your favour! You’ve shorted the heft of one activity and are starting the other with some success!
